         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00051"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">Wien XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard Beerhofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251"><hi rend="latintype">Hasenauerstraße 59</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00052"/>lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p><rs ref="#pmb2173" type="person">Olga</rs> liegt mit ihrer <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01736-1"/>Halsentzündg<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01736-1">Die Erkrankung stellte sich
               als Scharlach heraus, das anvisierte Treffen fand nicht statt, <ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L01738" subtype="cf"/>.</note> –<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o
               morgen nichts. Ich erwarte Ihre Ent<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheidg ob Sie <date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date> oder <date>Montag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>½ 6</time> kommen.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><date when="1907-12-06"><unclear>6</unclear>/12 907</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
